==軼事==
大會原擬邀請澳洲U23參賽，然而此青年隊因未能成軍而退賽，後邀得奧克蘭城頂上。最後更奪得冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2u23%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%9E%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%80%E6%AD%B2%E7%9B%83-074056834.html |title=澳洲U23退出雞年賀歲盃 |accessdate=2017-01-26 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202083202/https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2u23%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%9E%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%80%E6%AD%B2%E7%9B%83-074056834.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

主隊傑志因留力出戰亞洲賽，部份球員避戰，並邀請幾位其他球會的球員客串。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170128/s00006/1485569162025 |title=港超集氣傑志誓響頭炮 |accessdate=2017-01-30 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202064347/http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170128/s00006/1485569162025 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

